===Etymology===
The semantics may have developed along the grammaticalisation process "bamboo stalk" ([[箇]]) > "piece, item" > "classifier for every category of noun" > "possessive particle, generic particle". If so, it would then possibly be cognate with {{zh-l|竿|bamboo, rod}}. Compare {{etyl|bo|-}} {{l|bo|མཁར་བ}}, {{l|bo|འཁར་བ||walking stick, staff}} and {{etyl|th|-}} {{l|th|ก้าน||stem, stalk}}.

